00:39:15.770 --> 00:39:17.260 align:middle line:90%
So there's something about that.

00:39:17.260 --> 00:39:19.360 align:middle line:84%
There's an element,
these dueling dragons.

00:39:19.360 --> 00:39:21.850 align:middle line:84%
Like, yes, there has
to be the challenge.

00:39:21.850 --> 00:39:24.850 align:middle line:84%
There's the pressure on the
coal that creates the diamond.

00:39:24.850 --> 00:39:27.440 align:middle line:84%
