00:40:17.440 --> 00:40:19.840 align:middle line:84%
Let's make way for
the next thing.

00:40:19.840 --> 00:40:24.070 align:middle line:84%
And in a sense, I agree,
or I understand the logic,

00:40:24.070 --> 00:40:26.920 align:middle line:84%
