out the accountability

00:40:26.920 --> 00:40:31.720 align:middle line:84%
is, where are you taking care
of you in the here and now?

00:40:31.720 --> 00:40:34.732 align:middle line:84%
What is your soul telling you in
the here and now is important.

00:40:34.732 --> 00:40:36.190 align:middle line:84%
>>MEREDITH: Are
you even listening?

00:40:36.190 --> 00:40:37.065 align:middle line:90%
>>BEN STEWART: Right.

00:40:37.065 --> 00:40:39.430 align:middle line:84%
Because the hugest thing
about the transhuman thing

00:40:39.430 --> 00:40:41.477 align:middle line:84%
is the removal of our
own accountability.

00:40:41.477 --> 00:40:42.310 align:middle line:90%
>>MEREDITH: Exactly.

00:40:42.310 --> 00:40:43.450 align:middle line:84%
>>BEN STEWART: And
that feels great.

00:40:43.450 --> 00:40:45.310 align:middle line:84%
>>MEREDITH: Overwriting
internal messages

00:40:45.310 --> 00:40:46.325 align:middle line:90%
with external messaging.

00:40:46.325 --> 00:40:47.200 align:middle line:90%
>>BEN STEWART: Right.

00:40:47.200 --> 00:40:51.730 align:middle line:84%
And so, the very crucial
important task of the artist,

00:40:51.730 --> 00:40:53.620 align:middle line:90%
nowadays, are--

00:40:53.620 --> 00:40:55.870 align:middle line:84%
I mean, especially
right now in history

00:40:55.870 --> 00:40:59.650 align:middle line:84%
is, at this important
juncture, to get back

00:40:59.650 --> 00:41:01.900 align:middle line:84%
to some of the primal
meeting places,

00:41:01.900 --> 00:41:04.310 align:middle line:84%
where the artist would
always come out as well.

00:41:04.310 --> 00:41:07.540 align:middle line:84%
So cultivate the environment
where the artist always

00:41:07.540 --> 00:41:09.970 align:middle line:84%
seems to emerge, and
that's community.

